      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LEGEND\nRed arrows: SSH access path (Internet → PIP → VM)\nBlue arrows: Agent API calls (VM → Foundry / Entra)\nOrange arrows: Weather tool calls (VM → Function FQDN)\nGreen arrows: MCP calls (VM → CAE, VNet-internal)\nPurple dashed: Private Link connections (PE → Service)\nGray dashed: Image pull (ACR → CAE)\nYellow dashed: VNet Integration (Function outbound)\nRegion: eastus2  |  Subscription: ME-MngEnvMCAP687688\nAgent: pce (asst_fAVIpp16oVnfHaBuCo1BtvJ9)  |  6 function tools",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LEGEND\nRed arrows: SSH access path (Internet → PIP → VM)\nBlue arrows: Agent API calls (VM → Foundry / Entra)\nOrange arrows: Weather tool calls (VM → Function FQDN)\nGreen arrows: MCP calls (VM → CAE, VNet-internal)\nPurple dashed: Private Link connections (PE → Service)\nGray dashed: Image pull (ACR → CAE)\nYellow dashed: VNet Integration (Function outbound)\nRegion: eastus2  |  Subscription: ME-MngEnvMCAP687688\nAgent: pce (asst_fAVIpp16oVnfHaBuCo1BtvJ9)  |  6 function tools",
